title: Libera, St Philips Boys Choir, Angel Voices
description:
Libera history is among other things the road from the start as
St Philips Boys Choir, the transformation to Angel Voices and 
finally to the Libera of today.

This torrent covers that road and includes: 

21 early Videocaptures mostly from the BBC program "Thora on the 
straight and narrow" from the early 90:ties which means that the 
captures does not have the resolution or quality of today but they 
are very much enjoyable.

The following albums are included:

St Philips boys Choir- Sing forever
Angel Voices, New Day,1990
Angel Voices,1993
Angel Voices 2,1996
Angel Voices 3,1997
